data.description: ***Seller will pay for all title costs with an estimated value of $3000***     Welcome to a slice of paradise in Parrish's coveted Isles at Bayview community! This splendid 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence is a haven of simple elegance, offering a seamless blend of comfort and style with the charm of beautiful lake views. Only 2 years old!    Step inside to discover an open concept that fills the living spaces with abundant natural light, creating an inviting and airy ambiance. The heart of this home is its seamless flow, allowing you to move effortlessly from the dining area to the screened-in lanai. Picture yourself sipping your morning coffee or entertaining friends while enjoying picturesque views of the serene lake—making every moment a celebration of Florida's beauty.    Your perfect retreat is in the owner's suite, strategically positioned on the opposite side of the house for enhanced privacy. Revel in the luxury of a walk-in closet and wake up to peaceful lake views, creating a tranquil oasis within your own home.    Convenience takes center stage in this residence, as the community pool, clubhouse, playground, dog park, and mailboxes are just a leisurely stroll away. Enjoy a lifestyle of leisure and community connection, with every amenity at your fingertips.    This residence is not just a house; it's a lifestyle. With easy access to I-75 and the Ellenton Premium Outlet Mall, you'll find the perfect balance between local charm and premier shopping destinations. Florida living has never been more inviting.    Make your move to comfort and style in the heart of Parrish. This home is an embodiment of relaxed elegance, where every detail has been thoughtfully curated for a life well-lived. Welcome home to your sanctuary in the Isles at Bayview!
